  "_design_notes": [
    "Structure mirrors TH7 PCB mid-bosses: NonSpell → SpellCard → NonSpell → SpellCard → NonSpell → Final SpellCard.",
    "Movement uses phaseStartTick offset so each phase begins at centre with sin(0)=0 - no position jumps.",
    "NonSpell phases: sparse aimed/ring; recognisable but survivable - the WARM-UP before the card.",
    "SpellCard phases: dense, visually distinctive, timed bonus. Difficulty tiers: Easy=900t, Normal=700t, Hard=480t, Lunatic=260t.",
    "Cooldown units are server ticks (20 TPS). DifficultyConfig.speedMult/densityMult scales bullet speed/count.",
    "Pattern reference (PatternEngine): SPIRAL, AIMED, RING, SPREAD, DENSE_RING"
  ],

